Sale_Data_Analysis
Sales Data Analysis Project - Comprehensive EDA, visualization, and insights using Python, Excel, and Power BI. Perfect for portfolio showcasing data analytics skills.

ğŸ“Š Overview
Yeh project ek fictional retail company ke sales data ka analysis karta hai (12 months CSV files). Key insights:

Top performing products/regions

Monthly trends & revenue patterns

Customer segmentation

Data cleaning (missing values via MODE/MEDIAN)

Tools Used: Python (Pandas, Matplotlib), Excel (Mean/Median/Mode), Power BI Dashboard (6-8 charts)

ğŸ“ˆ Key Findings
Best month: December (holiday sales peak)

Top product: iPhone (highest revenue)

Best city: San Francisco

30% orders multiple products ke saath

ğŸ› ï¸ Tech Stack
text
Python: Pandas, NumPy, Seaborn, Matplotlib
Excel: AVERAGE, MEDIAN, MODE formulas
Power BI: Line/Bar charts, Maps, KPI cards
SQL: Joins for multi-file analysis (optional)
ğŸ“ Dataset
Source: Kaggle Superstore Sales (12 CSV files ~100k rows)

Columns: Order ID, Product, Quantity, Price Each, Order Date, Address

Size: 1 year (2019), ~260MB

Download: Kaggle Sales Data

