ğŸ“‹ Analysis Steps
Data Loading & Cleaning

Concat 12 CSVs

Handle missing (MODE for categories)

Parse dates, create Revenue column (Price * Quantity)

EDA

text
Best Month: df.groupby('Month')['Revenue'].sum()
Top Products: df['Product'].value_counts()
Visualizations

Line chart: Monthly revenue

Bar: Top 10 products

Heatmap: City vs Product

Power BI Dashboard

6 charts: Trends, Geo-map, KPI gauges

ğŸ“Š Sample Code Snippets
python
# Mean revenue per product
df.groupby('Product')['Revenue'].mean()

# MODE for missing category
mode_val = df['Category'].mode()[0]
df['Category'].fillna(mode_val, inplace=True)
